import React from "react";
import { Form, Input, Button, Checkbox, notification } from "antd";
import { UserOutlined, LockOutlined } from "@ant-design/icons";

import "./RegisterForm.scss";
import FormItem from "antd/lib/form/FormItem";

export default function RegisterForm() {
  return (
    <Form className="register-form">
      <Form.Item>
        <Input
          type="email"
          name="email"
          placeholder="Email"
          className="register-form-input"
          prefix={<UserOutlined style={{ color: "rgba(168, 171, 174 )" }} />}
        />
      </Form.Item>
      <Form.Item>
        <Input
          type="password"
          name="password"
          placeholder="Contraseña"
          className="register-form-input"
          prefix={<LockOutlined style={{ color: "rgba(168, 171, 174 )" }} />}
        />
      </Form.Item>
      <Form.Item>
        <Input
          type="password"
          name="repeatPassword"
          placeholder="Repita su contraseña"
          className="register-form-input"
          prefix={<LockOutlined style={{ color: "rgba(168, 171, 174 )" }} />}
        />
      </Form.Item>
      <Form.Item>
        <Checkbox name="privatePolicy">
          He leido y acepto la politica de privacidad.
        </Checkbox>
      </Form.Item>
      <Form.Item>
        <Button htmlType="reset" className="register-form-button">
          Borrar
        </Button>
        <Button htmlType="submit" className="register-form-button">
          Crear cuenta
        </Button>
      </Form.Item>
    </Form>
  );
}
